{"tid":887994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌佢老母 支共又搞事: 北韓籲美解除制裁 揚言恢復發展核武","createTime":"2018-11-03T11:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T00:43:10.000Z","uid":125193,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fe2f4267094acf0a99d0ef73110f3ee9c18b6d77","tid":887994,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T11:27:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201811030099.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F201811030099.aspx&d=PW3Ylk1m1Fd%2FEhJoOayKxMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=772436d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201811030099.aspx</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n北韓外交部2日警告，如果美國沒有解除針對北韓的經濟制裁，平壤可能將恢復加強核武的國家政策。圖為北韓領導人金正恩</span></strong><br />\n（中央社首爾3日綜合外電報導）北韓外交部昨晚發表聲明警告，如果美國沒有解除針對北韓的經濟制裁，平壤可能將恢復加強核武的國家政策。<br />\n<br />\n美國與南韓之間瀰漫一股不安氣氛，對於運用制裁與施壓北韓放棄核子計畫似乎不同調。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社報導，北韓外交部聲明表示，如果美國不改變立場，北韓可能恢復同時推動核武與經濟發展的「並進」政策。<br />\n<br />\n南韓本來建議解除部分對北韓的單邊制裁，以創造外交斡旋空間，但美國總統川普直接反駁，聲稱沒有經過華府批准，南韓不會付諸行動後，首爾當局上個月收回提議。（譯者：張曉雯/核稿：盧映孜）1071103<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181c01d32e855debd5934d4ad0e869d324203574","tid":887994,"uid":26329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T00:05:28.000Z","msg":"你放棄先<br />\n你唔制裁先<br />\n無限loop<br />\nloop到金仔死果日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc99be1de1497a9ca63582f4ee3f66a298be074","tid":887994,"uid":24730,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T00:08:15.000Z","msg":"入嚟想睇支共點搞事，但篇報導冇講喎"},{"pid":"db65d81ad3513f743d254a6434e1b6ff4c9afe73","tid":887994,"uid":195570,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T00:08:37.000Z","msg":"南韓真係無face, 靠美國呢個世界永遠無愛與和平"},{"pid":"c8562038d1f5d92d992f2a86c8f924dbd18f3c3b","tid":887994,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T00:28:04.000Z","msg":"想嚇侵侵，咁你咪試下囉。"},{"pid":"88c9217acf3d9f7e76465de421228a04cbc7f8e4","tid":887994,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecc99be1de1497a9ca63582f4ee3f66a298be074","tid":887994,"uid":24730,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T00:08:15.000Z","msg":"入嚟想睇支共點搞事，但篇報導冇講喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T00:32:09.000Z","msg":"我估可能做左中間人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 教唆金仔？"},{"pid":"10545cd6126cfea5ebaa3c6ac6195acbb9dd61c4","tid":887994,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T00:36:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73977fe35bec0a0042b026f2f756f38354d4d4b7","tid":887994,"uid":103513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T00:43:10.000Z","msg":"又趁大選係度搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}